\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {\textup  {\textsc  {PRISM}}{} at a glance.} A dense trajectory is filtered into multiple admissible soup families by validation loss, locality, and a fixed search budget. Within each family, \textup  {\textsc  {PRISM}}{} computes exact hidden-subpopulation regret over actual soups on a disjoint support split, then chooses the family-action pair with smallest structural-risk score.}}{2}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
